step_data.thought:
I see I'm currently on a page for creating a new product. This isn't the right place to find existing products that are visible in both Catalog and Search. I need to go back to the products listing page.

Looking at the current page structure, I can see a 'Back' button with ID '901' that will likely take me back to the products listing. From there, I can look for ways to filter or search for products with the visibility setting 'Catalog, Search'.

I notice that in the form I'm currently viewing, there's a visibility dropdown that has 'Catalog, Search' selected as the default value. This confirms that 'Catalog, Search' is a valid visibility setting that I need to look for in existing products.
